---
title: Gochujang Pork Chops with Bok Choy and Wok-Style Rice
description: Bring on the heat! Gochujang-basted pork chops make for a flavour bomb. Quick, crispy wok-style rice with garlicky bok choy add balance to this takeout-inspired dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/gochujang-pork-chops-bba517b8.jpg
